headline: CrowdStrike Named a Leader in the 2025 IDC MarketScape: Worldwide Cloud-Native Application Protection Platforms (CNAPP)
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, June 25, 2025--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced it has been named a Leader in the IDC MarketScape: Worldwide Cloud-Native Application Protection Platform 2025 Vendor Assessment1. We believe this recognition underscores CrowdStrike’s innovation and leadership in securing modern hybrid environments, as the only CNAPP delivering unified, real-time protection across cloud, identity, and endpoint.
